WEBVTT

00:07.000 --> 00:09.000
 <i>- Previously, on</i> The Borgias...

00:09.000 --> 00:11.300
- [Whispering]: I have waited
a lifetime for this moment.

00:11.300 --> 00:14.534
I will not forgive failure...
- We will not fail you,
Father.

00:14.534 --> 00:17.801
- Maybe Papa will
become pope, and you can
be who you want to be.

00:17.801 --> 00:20.300
- I shall fight you.
- With any means at my disposal.

00:20.300 --> 00:23.000
- I do tend to win
whatever battles I fight.

00:23.000 --> 00:26.501
- Cardinal Borgia has
the required majority.

00:26.501 --> 00:29.567
- You're not in
mourning, mother.
- But perhaps I am.

00:29.567 --> 00:32.868
- What are we gaining?
- Does Papa have
so many enemies?

00:32.868 --> 00:35.868
- As our father, perhaps not.
But as pope...

00:35.868 --> 00:38.767
We have placed the papal
mitre in the hands of an ape.

00:38.767 --> 00:41.667
I beg you now to release me
of my vows.

00:41.667 --> 00:43.634
- I would be a prince of state,
Father.

00:43.634 --> 00:46.400
Juan can bear arms
for the Borgia family

00:46.400 --> 00:49.334
- But I swear, if God
does not protect us, I shall.

00:49.334 --> 00:52.033
- Whatever you're being paid,
I'll double it.

00:52.033 --> 00:54.868
- The pope cannot love?
- Not only must he be chaste;

00:54.868 --> 00:56.868
he must be seen
to be chaste.

00:56.868 --> 01:00.033
- Simony! I charge you now
in public!

01:00.033 --> 01:04.766
- They all want you dead.
- Serve this... to Orsini.

01:04.766 --> 01:06.434
- [Orsini]: Poison.
- Poison!

01:06.434 --> 01:08.667
- The poison was meant for us.
- You don't poison the pope!

01:08.667 --> 01:10.000
You poison a rabid dog!

01:10.000 --> 01:12.801
It offends nature, it offends
God Himself!

01:12.801 --> 01:14.400
- So, God will take
his revenge, then.
- With our help.

01:18.200 --> 01:22.033
***

